metadata.name: SOARadelic Visions
metadata.description: SOARadelic Visions is the genesis NFT of the KooyCollabs manifold contract. This piece is a collaboration between KooyCreates and Von Dough. Von Dough has a knack for abstract art specifically with a psychedelic style. The background in this piece was completely created by him. KooyCreates specializes in graffiti art with the moniker of SOAR. The lettering and outline effects were created by him. This piece serves as the entry point into the KooyCollabs universe and will come with unique perks for holders of this specific NFT.
